    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5487632/" class="title-link">资历压倒一切</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5487632"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bcbulang/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3213003-23.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bcbulang/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">边城不浪</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-07-01"
      class="main-meta">2012-07-01 21:22:15</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5487632_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                        PLA诸将里，公认林、粟、刘、彭、徐五位能力秀出同伦。但仅以战史而论，刘帅在解放战争里受制于挺进大别山的“浪漫主义”战略，被白崇禧追得满山跑，最后打黄维兵团还落得个“瘦狗拉硬屎”的自嘲；彭帅指挥得力于情报工作至巨，在西北的对手胡宗南军令未出，身为中共地下...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5487632/#comments">(15回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">27有用 / 2没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5487632_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5487632_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
